 St Paul Minnesota by the Twin City Observer St Paul Sun Publishing Co Inc Minneapolis Phone FE 93271 St Paul Phone CA 58825 SUBSCRIPTION RATES 200 Per Year Six Months 125 All Mail Subscriptions Payable in Advance Editorial and Business Offices at 858 Iglehart Ave St Paul Minnesota MILTON G WILLIAMS ESTYR BRADLEY PEAKE ROBERT A JONES Entered as second class matter October 11 1951 at the post office at St Paul 1 Minnesota under the act of March 3 1879 flcnv e Member National Editorial Association Minnesota Editorial Association National Newspaper Publishers Association EDITORIAL THE IMPORTANCE OF THE INDIVIDUAL in this period when it is the unthinking fashion to echo the sentiment that no one is indispensable was emphasized in dramatic manner early this week when President Eisenhower was stricken Apparently there is reason to believe as well as hope that the setback to his health was of minor importance and that recovery will be speedy as well as complete and for that all Americans are grateful Their prayers may"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2025-07-10T20:46:05.995Z", "group": ["ndnp/mnhi", "minnesota-historical-society-saint-paul-mn-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn84025909/1957-11-28/ed-1/?sp=4", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:mnhi:batch_mnhi_hamlet_ver01:data:sn84025909:00542865301:1957112801:0471/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=451&w=316", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:mnhi:batch_mnhi_hamlet_ver01:data:sn84025909:00542865301:1957112801:0471/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=902&w=632", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/mnhi/batch_mnhi_hamlet_ver01/data/sn84025909/00542865301/1957112801/0471.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 4, "language": ["english"], "location": ["saint paul", "minnesota", "ramsey", "united states"], "location_city": ["saint paul"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_county": ["r